    Safer, Easier Transport

    PICKUP

    We pick-up piano from pick-up location. (Don't try to do this yourself unless you have the help of a professional.)

    TRANSPORT

    The piano is transported to its destination, safe and secure, by our moving services.

    TUNING

    Once the piano has found its ideal place, we tune it up to make sure it is ready for you to start playing.
